gwt.g3d.client.shader
Class TextureShader

java.lang.Object
  gwt.g3d.client.shader.AbstractShader
      gwt.g3d.client.shader.TextureShader
All Implemented Interfaces:
GLDisposable, Shader
public class TextureShader
extends AbstractShader

Represents a simple shader that renders a texture. This shader contains the following variables: uniform mat4 uModelViewMatrix, uProjectionMatrix; uniform sampler2D uTexture; uniform vec4 uTintColor; attribute vec4 aPosition; attribute vec2 aTexCoord;

Author:
